<figureCitation box="[1113,1172,293,315]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–4" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1185,1208]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,229,1107]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[151,1436,229,1118]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–4. Pericaliella and Monstruncusarctia spp., males. 1, P. melanodisca, Uganda, Kibale; 2, P. popoudinae sp. n., holotype, Rwanda,Butare; 3, M.aurantiaca, Guinea, Kindia, 4, M. anikini sp. n., Uganda, Kibale." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1065724/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="578">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
